com.siemens.ct.exi
Class EncodingOptions

java.lang.Object
  com.siemens.ct.exi.EncodingOptions

public class EncodingOptions
extends java.lang.Object

Some applications may require EXI coding options shared via the EXI Header (e.g., EXI Cookie). This class allows one to specify which coding options are needed.

Version:
0.7
Author:
Daniel.Peintner.EXT@siemens.com, Joerg.Heuer@siemens.com
